text: you can fight with the Android framework as much as you want
and I wanted it a lot
but in the end there are some things you have to follow, regardless of MVVM, RxBinding and such
so there are behaviour bleeding for things like recyclerview, viewpager, or anything Intent-related
buuuuut not as large as you'd expect
as long as you keep your data immutable
that's the key: good data models that are also immutable
